                    <span>If you never read another line of text in your life, turn to page 169 of this book and read the last sentance.<p>Learn it, live it, and you'll be set for life.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Motivation</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
